#301
Entering the encampment~
You have entered a large encampment in the middle of the great plains. It
would seem that within, an army of some sort is preparing for an assualt
upon the nearby city of Tempra. To the south, you see a guard post formed
by two mobile sage towers upon either side of the path.
~
