#302
At the Guard Post~
You are standing at a checkpoint within the encampment.  To the east
and west, you see two siege towers which are being used as a mobile
barracks. Several guards stand within ready to aid thier comrads if need
be. To the south, there is a large bonfire, and to the north, the trail
continues onto the great plains.
