#303
The Eastern Guard Tower~
You are standing within a large mobile siege tower which has been
converted into a temporary barracks for the guards of the encampment. 
The floor is covered with piles of unwashed clothing and armor along with
scraps of food and other waste. The only part of this room that isn't
covered in refuse is a nicely kept weapon rack in the back corner, most
likely placed there by one of the higher ups in this force who is 
concerned enough about his or her wellbeing enough to ensure that these
grunts have adequate armorment.
~
